msgid ""
"`lib32` - Compatibility libraries for running 32-bit applications on a "
"64-bit version of FreeBSD."
msgstr "`lib32` - 在 64 位版本的 FreeBSD 上运行 32 位应用程序的兼容性库。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:404
