#, 
msgid "`Services` - Described in <<bsdinstall-sysconf>>."
msgstr "`Services` - 在 <<bsdinstall-sysconf>> 中进行了描述。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1114
#, 
