#,  no-wrap
msgid ""
"Menu showing that the installation has finished. And asking if you want to "
"open a shell to make manual changes."
msgstr "菜单显示安装已完成，并询问是否要打开一个 shell 来进行手动更改。"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1121
#,  no-wrap
